              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">AI Act (Reg. 2024/1689) + GDPR</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">2024</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Supranational regulation</td>
